### Get all categories (basic)
GET {{baseUrl}}/categories
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

### Get categories with pagination
GET {{baseUrl}}/categories?limit=5&page=1
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

### Get categories with filtering
GET {{baseUrl}}/categories?name=Electronics&isActive=true
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

### Get categories with sorting
GET {{baseUrl}}/categories?sort=name:asc
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

### Get categories with combined pagination, filtering, and sorting
GET {{baseUrl}}/categories?name=E&sort=name:asc,createdAt:desc&limit=10&page=1
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

### Test sorting with multiple fields
GET {{baseUrl}}/categories?sort=code:asc,name:desc
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

### Test sorting with invalid field (should be ignored)
GET {{baseUrl}}/categories?sort=invalidField:asc,name:desc
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

### Category by id
GET {{baseUrl}}/categories/1
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

### Create Category
POST {{baseUrl}}/categories
Content-Type: application/json
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

{
  "code": "ELEC",
  "name": "Electronics",
  "description": "Electronic items"
}
